      "sectionId": "s1",
      "title": "Getting%20the%20Context",
      "body": "%60%60%60js%0Aconst%20canvas%20%3D%20document.getElementById('myCanvas')%3B%0Aconst%20ctx%20%3D%20canvas.getContext('2d')%3B%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s2-3",
      "sectionId": "s2",
      "title": "Rectangles",
      "body": "%60%60%60js%0Actx.fillStyle%20%3D%20'red'%3B%0Actx.fillRect(10%2C%2010%2C%20150%2C%20100)%3B%20%2F%2F%20x%2C%20y%2C%20width%2C%20height%0A%0Actx.strokeStyle%20%3D%20'blue'%3B%0Actx.lineWidth%20%3D%205%3B%0Actx.strokeRect(200%2C%2010%2C%20150%2C%20100)%3B%20%2F%2F%20x%2C%20y%2C%20width%2C%20height%0A%0Actx.clearRect(15%2C%2015%2C%2030%2C%2030)%3B%20%2F%2F%20x%2C%20y%2C%20width%2C%20height%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-4",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "Lines",
      "body": "```js\nctx.beginPath();\nctx.moveTo(50, 50); // Starting point\nctx.lineTo(200, 50); // Ending point\nctx.lineTo(200, 200); // Next line ending point\nctx.closePath(); // Connects the end point to the start point\nctx.stroke();\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-5",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "Circles",
      "body": "%60%60%60js%0Actx.beginPath()%3B%0Actx.arc(150%2C%20150%2C%2075%2C%200%2C%202%20*%20Math.PI)%3B%20%2F%2F%20x%2C%20y%2C%20radius%2C%20startAngle%2C%20endAngle%0Actx.fillStyle%20%3D%20'green'%3B%0Actx.fill()%3B%0Actx.stroke()%3B%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s3-6",
      "sectionId": "s3",
      "title": "Arcs",
      "body": "```js\nctx.beginPath();\nctx.arc(150, 150, 75, 0, Math.PI); // x, y, radius, startAngle, endAngle\nctx.stroke();\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-7",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "Quadratic Curve",
      "body": "```js\nctx.beginPath();\nctx.moveTo(50, 250);\nctx.quadraticCurveTo(200, 100, 400, 250); // cpX, cpY, endX, endY\nctx.stroke();\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-8",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "Bezier Curve",
      "body": "```js\nctx.beginPath();\nctx.moveTo(50, 300);\nctx.bezierCurveTo(150, 100, 350, 500, 450, 300); // cp1X, cp1Y, cp2X, cp2Y, endX, endY\nctx.stroke();\n```"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-9",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "Text",
      "body": "%60%60%60js%0Actx.font%20%3D%20'30px%20Arial'%3B%0Actx.fillStyle%20%3D%20'black'%3B%0Actx.fillText('Hello%20Canvas'%2C%2010%2C%2050)%3B%20%2F%2F%20text%2C%20x%2C%20y%0A%0Actx.strokeText('Hello%20Canvas'%2C%2010%2C%20100)%3B%20%2F%2F%20text%2C%20x%2C%20y%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s4-10",
      "sectionId": "s4",
      "title": "Images",
      "body": "%60%60%60js%0Aconst%20img%20%3D%20new%20Image()%3B%0Aimg.src%20%3D%20'path%2Fto%2Fimage.jpg'%3B%0Aimg.onload%20%3D%20()%20%3D%3E%20%7B%0A%20%20ctx.drawImage(img%2C%2010%2C%2010)%3B%20%2F%2F%20img%2C%20x%2C%20y%0A%20%20ctx.drawImage(img%2C%2050%2C%2050%2C%20100%2C%20100)%3B%20%2F%2F%20img%2C%20x%2C%20y%2C%20width%2C%20height%0A%20%20ctx.drawImage(img%2C%20100%2C%20100%2C%20100%2C%20100%2C%20150%2C%20150%2C%20200%2C%20200)%3B%20%2F%2F%20img%2C%20sx%2C%20sy%2C%20sWidth%2C%20sHeight%2C%20dx%2C%20dy%2C%20dWidth%2C%20dHeight%0A%7D%3B%0A%60%60%60",
      "encoded": true
    },
    {
      "id": "s5-11",
      "sectionId": "s5",
      "title": "Translation",
      "body": "```js\nctx.translate(100, 100); // x, y\nctx.fillRect(0, 0, 50, 50);\n```"
